of married life,

7
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,869
but it's definitely yours.

8
00:00:54,019 --> 00:00:54,899
Think about this.

9
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:56,070
According to
traditional Chinese medicine,

10
00:00:56,220 --> 00:00:56,909
poor wealth

11
00:00:56,979 --> 00:00:58,030
makes one to be emotionally attached.

12
00:00:58,460 --> 00:00:59,459
You see,

13
00:00:59,460 --> 00:00:59,978
if you

14
00:00:59,979 --> 00:01:01,459
always lose yourself

15
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:02,350
in a relationship,

16
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:03,219
it's basically

17
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:04,589
because your liver is weak.

18
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:06,270
Prone to sacrifice for others

19
00:01:06,380 --> 00:01:07,498
