20
00:01:07,499 --> 00:01:08,338
comes from the mutual influence

21
00:01:08,339 --> 00:01:10,229
between the liver and lungs.

22
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,099
Indulging in fantasies

23
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:11,939
and

24
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,179
self-blame

25
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:14,338
is due to poor blood circulation.

26
00:01:14,339 --> 00:01:15,778
Overall,

27
00:01:15,779 --> 00:01:16,659
you're being a hopeless romantic

28
00:01:16,660 --> 00:01:17,379
because

29
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:18,309
you are sick.

30
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:20,229
I'm sick?

31
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,430
I thought I was just pathetic.

32
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:28,630
Don't sell yourself short.

33
00:01:31,499 --> 00:01:33,749
How are things going
with Gu Yancheng?

34
00:01:33,859 --> 00:01:34,739
Getting a divorce?

35
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:35,899
If you do,

36
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:36,899
I can also become

37
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:38,630
a divorce lawyer.

38
00:01:38,979 --> 00:01:40,389
I don't know.

39
00:01:40,699 --> 00:01:41,539
I only want to

40
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:43,469
get my thoughts straight.

41
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:45,949
Very well.

42
00:01:46,139 --> 00:01:47,229
Let's work on that together.

43
00:01:48,979 --> 00:01:51,258
Who's the boss here?

44
00:01:51,259 --> 00:01:53,229
I pay your salary.
Aren't you supposed to be working?

45
00:01:56,139 --> 00:01:57,190
Ouch.

46
