224
00:13:22,583 --> 00:13:24,746
I've prepared a gift for you both.

225
00:13:26,234 --> 00:13:27,255
Ms. Wen.

226
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,029
(Come to think of it,)

227
00:13:31,459 --> 00:13:32,458
(it seems)

228
00:13:32,459 --> 00:13:35,270
(that since she appeared as Su Xun,)

229
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,829
(my marriage with Gu Yancheng)

230
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:40,390
(has been slowly falling apart.)

231
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:50,139
I'll be a good person for once.

232
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,709
Here's a reminder.

233
00:13:52,779 --> 00:13:54,019
Do you think

234
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:55,990
your husband is only cheating on you?

235
00:13:59,059 --> 00:14:01,029
(Is she the one)

236
00:14:01,179 --> 00:14:02,709
(who called me anonymously?)

237
00:14:04,059 --> 00:14:06,949
(What's her relationship
with Gu Yancheng?)

238
00:14:19,819 --> 00:14:20,870
Ms. Wang,

239
00:14:22,140 --> 00:14:23,259
I'd like to ask

240
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:25,189
for Su Xun's address.

241
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:26,418
She took sick leave.

242
00:14:26,419 --> 00:14:27,949
I want to visit her.

243
00:14:30,059 --> 00:14:31,630
I'll wait for your message.

244
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,270
Thank you.

245
00:14:45,059 --> 00:14:46,390
Wen Ruoyun,

246
00:14:46,539 --> 00:14:47,870
I've been searching everywhere for you.

247
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,590
And here you are.

248
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:52,789
Do you think I need to hide from you?

249
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,919
♪That crimson stain on the collar♪

250
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:07,590
♪That alluring scent♪

251
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:12,999
♪All excuses sound so pale and empty♪

252
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,670
♪What cruel sarcasm♪

253
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:23,239
♪Oh, women, they never learn♪

254
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:27,430
♪When your heart flutters,
it's bound to be broken eventually♪

255
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,959
♪Midnight, a piercing chill♪

256
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:33,630
♪Wakes you up from a shattered dream♪

257
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,919
♪Heavy mist shrouds the truth♪

258
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,919
♪A steadfast retaliation comes alive♪

259
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:43,990
♪Oh, men, those smarty-pants♪

260
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:47,319
♪The backfire of your overflowing charm♪

261
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:51,110
♪Has no mercy♪

262
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:54,679
♪May your life be barren♪

263
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,959
♪May you tread on a thorny path alone♪

264
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,439
♪May you vanish into thin air♪

265
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,159
♪Lies will adorn your tombstone♪

266
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:02,639
♪Release me from this hatred♪

267
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,870
♪Free me from this excruciating cage♪

268
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,439
♪Let me go to light♪

269
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,999
♪Let's never meet again♪

270
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,479
♪When I use your words♪

271
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,439
♪And your ways♪

272
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,839
♪You blame me for being cruel♪

273
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:16,839
♪Life is ironic♪

274
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,319
♪I want your end♪

275
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,399
♪To be lonely♪

276
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:22,270
♪With no one to hate♪

277
00:16:22,400 --> 00:16:26,110
♪You will live in endless nightmares♪

278
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,910
♪Rise♪

279
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:50,230
♪From the ashes♪
